<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hoist" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hoist,</orth> to draw up (sails): <cit><quote>I have --ed sail to all the winds,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 117.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 117, 7</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. err 5.21" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. V, 21</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 1.5.215" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 5, 215</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 3.10.15" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 10, 15</bibl>. With <emph>up,</emph> == to lift up: <cit><quote>and h. thee up to the shouting plebeians,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 4.12.34" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 12, 34</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.55" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 55</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>